xfce4-places-plugin v0.1 released

 * Adds i18n support
 * Fixes url escaping bug (#3027)
 * Fixes hard-coded thunar path (#3053)

2007-03-14
================================================================================
xfce4-places-plugin v0.0.9 released

 * Reads and watches .gtk-bookmarks for changes
